SELECT [c].[ContractId], [c].[ContractName], [c].[ContractNumber]
FROM [Contract] AS [c]
WHERE ([c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL OR [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (

    FROM [Project] AS [p]
    WHERE [c].[ContractId] = [p].[ContractId]) = 0
